<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Canva Magic Studio is the best free AI tools for content creation for visual assets. Its AI features, including text-to-image, Magic Expand, Background Remover, and Magic Design are accessible on the free plan.</span></p>
<h4><span style="font-weight: 400;">Key Features</span></h4>
