</ul>
<h4><span style="font-weight: 400;">Pricing</span></h4>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Free plan with broad feature access. Canva Pro at $15/month. Teams plan at $10/month per user (3-person minimum).</span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Opus Clip: The Ultimate Best AI Tools for YouTube Content Creation</span></h3>
<div id="attachment_203173" style="width: 2570px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-203173" class="wp-image-203173 size-full" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Image-from-Opus-Clip-scaled.jpg" alt="Opus Clip: The Ultimate Best AI Tools for YouTube Content Creation" width="2560" height="1434" /><p id="caption-attachment-203173" class="wp-caption-text">Image from Opus Clip</p></div>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Opus Clip is the best AI tools for YouTube content creation and short-form repurposing, automatically identifying the most engaging moments from long-form video and cutting them into platform-ready clips with virality scores.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Opus Clip is the leading best AI tools for YouTube content creation platform for creators who produce long-form video and need to repurpose it into TikToks, Reels, and YouTube Shorts. It is the most cost-effective best AI tools for video content creation entry point for high-volume repurposers.</span></p>
<h4><span style="font-weight: 400;">Key Features</span></h4>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Auto-clip detection: AI identifies the most engaging, emotionally resonant moments for short-form clips</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Virality scoring: Each clip receives a predicted engagement score before you export</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Dynamic captions: Auto-generated, styled captions with speaker identification and word highlighting</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Speaker framing: Automatically reframes horizontal video to vertical with the speaker centered</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">B-roll generation: AI adds contextually relevant B-roll clips to enhance talking-head content</span></li>
