<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Every reputable gold dealers on this list holds an A+ BBB rating and has operated for multiple years with documented customer reviews. According to </span><a href="https://www.goldinvestinghub.com/best/best-place-to-buy-gold-online-top-7-dealers-reviewed-by-premiums-security/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener external noreferrer" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Gold Investing Hub&#8217;s scam prevention guide</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">, a verifiable physical address (not a PO box), a documented operating history of at least three years, and a minimum of several hundred verified customer reviews are the baseline checks for any best gold dealers you consider.</span></p>
