<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">For local purchasing, the best gold dealers near me search depends on your city. For orders under $1,000, Money.com&#8217;s dealer guide recommends using their local directory to find verified buyers in all 50 US states. For amounts above $1,000, the best gold dealers online consistently offer lower premiums, more competitive pricing, and more payment options than most local coin shops.</span></p>
