]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">An innovative bridge to institutional credit markets is officially launching in the Web3 ecosystem. Binance Wallet is thrilled to host the exclusive </span><b>Token Generation Event (TGE) for Cap (CAP)</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> on the BNB Smart Chain, organized in direct partnership with PancakeSwap. Operating on a decentralized allocation framework, this premier launch event allows eligible users to commit Binance Coin (BNB) to secure early-stage token placement with no vesting schedules.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The subscription window is exceptionally brief and precise, opening on </span><b>June 26, 2026, from 10:00 AM to 12:00 PM (UTC)</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">. Because token allocation is calculated proportionally against the final collective capital pool, understanding the exact eligibility and structural rules is vital. Read on to find the complete operational breakdown of this exclusive TGE event.</span></p>
<p><b><i>More Active Trading Programs: </i></b><a href="https://ventureburn.com/binance-alpha-kgen-trading-competition-594000-kgen/" data-wpel-link="internal"><b><i>Binance Alpha Launches KGeN (KGEN) Trading Competition With $200,000 Reward Pool</i></b></a></p>
<h2><b>Details of the Cap (CAP) Token Generation Event</b></h2>
<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-77019" src="https://chainplay.gg/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/782144f44cab300a2d81f3714c6465026309a137fd1ff9466f5e15fdac04af68.jpeg" alt="" width="1600" height="900" /></p>
