<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">June 26, 2026 | 10:00 AM &#8211; 12:00 PM (UTC)</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><b>Accepted Subscription Asset</b></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">BNB</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><b>Price Per Token</b></td>
